{"tid":808322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=?? 地盤釘板工墮樓亡　勞工處發停工通知書","createTime":"2018-09-06T08:49:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-06T11:00:52.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ddd8e2b7eb8255f10b792383cc507469baf942dd","tid":808322,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T08:49:07.000Z","msg":"牛頭角彩福邨第三期及體育館地盤，今晨（6日）8時許發生奪命工業意外，一名姓林（40歲）釘板工人從1樓的缺口墮下，當場陷入昏迷，被送往聯合醫院搶救後不治，其親友接獲消息後，於下午2時許到醫院了解情況，警方及勞工處正就事件展開調查。據了解，該名工人未婚，從事釘板工作1年多。從照片可見，事發後已有人在該缺口上放上一塊木板，旁邊遺有一頂疑屬於死者的安全帽，而懷疑為死者倒臥的位置，則被人以膠帶圍封。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180906/photo/bkn-20180906133726488-0906_00822_001_04b.jpg?20180906161449\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180906%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180906133726488-0906_00822_001_04b.jpg%3F20180906161449&h=06db1b55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180906/bkn-20180906133726488-0906_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180906%2Fbkn-20180906133726488-0906_00822_001.html&d=cDinVvufwTKkQuZWXBaguIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=a977d1d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180906/bkn-20180906133726488-0906_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"c6155be3d1b0028ddefd2027c5514f6f64bdb7d1","tid":808322,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T08:50:43.000Z","msg":"慘"},{"pid":"fc85fdf9b6cdee30d0b57d00ec72b5615dede214","tid":808322,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T08:54:33.000Z","msg":"殺人放火建制派<br />\n修橋舖路無屍骸"},{"pid":"de4d3f0061649752ada034fe4a9462c6dcce48ad","tid":808322,"uid":46649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T10:23:50.000Z","msg":"真係搵命搏"},{"pid":"4e7b1257ac0ab50690272e5f84723f5e43cf64fe","tid":808322,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"r